{
  "texts": [
    "GraphAide curates multi-source data and constructs ontology-guided knowledge graphs to address the challenges faced by baseline LLM-only applications.",
    "The platform also provides efficient data persistence, enabling interactions via a natural language questionanswering interface.",
    "GraphAide combines a robust graph matching approach with the semantic similarity provided by vector databases to enhance the accuracy and explainability of LLM-generated responses.",
    "Developed as an extensible agentic RAG application, GraphAide reuses data ingestion, entity disambiguation, storage, query, and reasoning components throughout the application lifecycle.",
    "Key capabilities of GraphAide include:"
  ]
}